{"tid":884171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國又要選舉，係時候將反侵撚一個一個摘名恥笑","createTime":"2018-10-31T11:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T12:58:33.000Z","uid":123264,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e4455b21d2d6b7776ecf872da0b0fac8db7db8c5","tid":884171,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"一到選舉成班弱智就好似蟲仔咁走哂出黎<br />\n拎住個上個大選錯到仆街既民調圍爐<br />\n上個大選預測結果最準既拉斯穆森民調又隻字不提<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbb63ab18a5a27f6848dbb25a224115867caa14","tid":884171,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4455b21d2d6b7776ecf872da0b0fac8db7db8c5","tid":884171,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"一到選舉成班弱智就好似蟲仔咁走哂出黎<br />\n拎住個上個大選錯到仆街既民調圍爐<br />\n上個大選預測結果最準既拉斯穆森民調又隻字不提<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:47:10.000Z","msg":"今次個民調係點？"},{"pid":"d09f0c1b1cf86e857c841b9adc17c4fe87e3d1e4","tid":884171,"uid":162272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:58:33.000Z","msg":"2018年10月31日，星期三<br />\n<br />\n距離選舉日還有不到一周的時間，民主黨人在共和黨人的通用國會選票上領先三分，這項調查的誤差幅度為+/- 2個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n最新的拉斯穆森報告電話和在線調查發現，如果國會選舉今天舉行，47％的可能美國選民會選擇民主黨候選人。百分之四十四（44％）會選擇共和黨人。百分之三（3％）更喜歡其他候選人，百分之六（6％）尚未決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rasmussenreports.com/public_content/politics/mood_of_america/generic_congressional_ballot_oct31\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rasmussenreports.com%2Fpublic_content%2Fpolitics%2Fmood_of_america%2Fgeneric_congressional_ballot_oct31&d=9f0LvOTZOOmviRGUWSaTmHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=b0959964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rasmussenreports.com/public_content/politics/mood_of_america/generic_congressional_ballot_oct31</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">貼拉斯穆森民調俾你睇，滿意未?</span>"}]}